<p>The calculations in this guide are educational illustrations, not tax advice. If your income is complex -- multiple clients, business expenses, depreciation, a mix of W-2 and 1099 -- working with a CPA for at least one year pays for itself in avoided penalties and properly optimized deductions.</p>

